                <div FwObjectId="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" FWContainerID ContainerName="clKeyResourceList" name="ctl11$clKeyResourceList_" IsModified="False" ContentOperation="None" FWContainerType="CLContentDataView" FWObjectType="Content" serverid="ctl11$clKeyResourceList" hiddenControlID="ctl11_clKeyResourceList_hiddenField" ViewCssClass="CLContentDataView" IsVisible="True" id="ctl11_clKeyResourceList" class="CLContentDataView">
	<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-16"?><dl class="deflist-Boxed"><dt class="toggleLink">Acne and rosacea</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>Is it acne or rosacea? One of the most common signs of rosacea, bumps, and pimples, is also one of the most common causes of confusion about the skin condition.</p> <p><a href="/public/diseases/acne-and-rosacea" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Learn more</a></p></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Bumps and growths</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>There are a number of skin conditions that cause bumps and growths to appear on the surface or just below the skin.</p> <p> <a href="/public/diseases/bumps-and-growths" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Learn more</a></p></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Color problems in your skin</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>Irregular areas in which there are changes in skin color are a common problem with a wide array of potential causes.</p> <p> <a href="/public/diseases/color-problems" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Learn more</a></p></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Contagious skin diseases</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>Learn which types of skin diseases are contagious. </p> <ul>     <li> <a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/athlete-s-foot-how-to-prevent" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/athlete-s-foot-how-to-prevent,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Athlete's foot: How to prevent</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/cold-sores">Cold sores</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/genital-herpes/genital-herpes">Genital herpes</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/genital-warts" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/genital-warts,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Genital warts</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/head-lice" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/head-lice,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Head lice</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/herpes-simplex" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/herpes-simplex,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Herpes simplex</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/impetigo">Impetigo</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/molluscum-contagiosum" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/molluscum-contagiosum,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Molluscum contagiosum</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/nail-fungus">Nail fungus</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/ringworm">Ringworm</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/scabies" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/scabies,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Scabies</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/shingles" returnvalue="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/shingles,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch">Shingles</a></li>     <li><a href="/public/diseases/contagious-skin-diseases/warts">Warts</a></li> </ul></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Cosmetic treatments</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>From chemical peels, botox, and fillers, find out which cosmetic treatment is right for you and what questions you should ask before getting a cosmetic treatment.</p> <p> <a href="/public/diseases/cosmetic-treatments" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Learn more</a></p></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Dry / sweaty skin</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>Do you have really dry or excessively sweaty skin? Find out the causes of your symptoms and learn how you can manage your condition.</p> <ul>     <li><a returnvalue="/public/diseases/dry-sweaty-skin/dry-skin,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch" href="/public/diseases/dry-sweaty-skin/dry-skin">Dry skin</a></li>     <li><a style="color: #0078bf; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-family: Open Sans,arial,sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-align: start; letter-spacing: normal;" href="/public/diseases/eczema/hand-eczema/hand-eczema">Dry, scaly, and painful hands could be hand eczema</a></li>     <li><a returnvalue="/public/diseases/dry-sweaty-skin/hyperhidrosis,,ExternalURL,_self,,,false,false,false,false,,;NoWatch" href="/public/diseases/dry-sweaty-skin/hyperhidrosis">Hyperhidrosis</a></li> </ul></dd><dt class="toggleLink">Eczema / dermatitis</dt><dd class="toggleLinkTarget is-hidden"><p>Eczema and dermatitis are terms for a group of skin conditions that cause the skin to become inflamed or irritated. <script>
    function search(valThis) {
        $("#lblNoResults").hide();
        if (valThis == "") {
            $('ul#conditionSearchId > li').show();
        } else {
            $('ul#conditionSearchId > li').each(function () {
                var text = $(this).text().toLowerCase();
                if (text.indexOf(valThis) >= 0) {
                    $(this).show()
                }
                else {
                    $(this).hide();
                }
            });
        };

        if ($('ul#conditionSearchId li:visible').length == 0) {
            $("#lblNoResults").show();
        }
    }

    // Wire search
    $("#ctl11_txtCommonConditions").keyup(function () {
        var valThis = $(this).val().toLowerCase();
        search(valThis);
    });

    $(document).ready(function () {
        // Show all "Common Conditions" but hide after 10 (0-9) as we have no room. Show on KeyPress
        search($("#ctl11_txtCommonConditions").val());
        $('ul#conditionSearchId li:gt(9)').hide();
    });
</script>
